Very tasty dish. I substituted sherry for white wine but it did not make any difference to the flavour as it was a small amount anyway. It has nice colour and texture and produced a thick sauce that went well with rice. Depending on the curry you use it can be a spicy dish but as I like it that way I was very happy with the turnout! Would definitely make this again!

